## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date and comprehensive data on the incidence of heart attacks among athletes. The potential impact of COVID-19 vaccinations is still under investigation, and conclusions drawn from current data may change as more information becomes available. Additionally, the focus on high-profile cases may skew public perception of the prevalence of these events. Further research is needed to establish a clearer understanding of the causes and prevention of heart attacks in athletes.

